{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Joâſs perſuhſe to Samarijaſ/ (un waldija) feſch-\nKUNGU/ un tas KUNGS pa- padeſmitis Gaddus.\npaſſtija to/ jo wiſch uſſuhkoja\nIſraêta Spaïdiſchanu/ ar ko tas\nSihreru Kehniſch tohs ſpaïdija."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS dewe Iſraêtam weenu Peſtitaju/ ka\ntee no to Sihreru Rohkas iſ-\nſprukke/ un tee Iſraêka Behrni\ndſihwoja faiwâs Teltis/ ta ka\npirnak."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tatſchu tee ne atſtabjehs no Jerobeama Namma Greb-\nkeem/ kas Iſraêlu grehkoht dar-\nrijs/ bet wiſch ſtaigaja eekſch\nteem : Ir tas Eika Meſch palik-\nke eekſch Samarijas."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo no Joâſa Lautiin ne bija waiaſk atliſkuschi/ ka veez-\nDeſmits Jahtneeki/ un deſmits Ratti/ un deſmits tuhſtroſchi\nRahjineeki. Jo tas Kehniſch no Sihrîjas bij tohs nokawis/\nun tohs darrijs ka Kuhleja Put-\ntektus."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kaſ wehl no Joâſa Lee-\ntahm atteek/ un wiſch/ ko wiſch\nirr darrijs/ un wiſch winna\nSpehks/ tas irr rakſtihts to\nIſraêta Kehnitau Laiku-Grah-\nmatâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Joâſs atſmitge ar fa-\nweem Tehweem/ un tappe eekſch\nSamarijaſaprakts. Un winna\nDehls Joas tappe par Kehnituu\nwinna Weeta."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Trihsdeſmits ſeptitâ\nRaddâ Joas ta Kehnixa no Ju-\ntappe Joas Joâſa Dehls\nKehnituu pahr Iſraêlu eekſch"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſch darrija/ ka tam KUNGAM ne patieke\nwiſch ne atſtabjebs no wiſſeen\nJerobeama Neebata Dehl\nGrehkeem/ kas Iſraêlu grehko-\ndarrijs/ eekſch teem wiſch sta-\ngaja."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kaſ weht no Joaſ\nLeetahm atteek/ un wiſch ko wiſſe-\nirr darrijs/ un wiſch winna\nSpehks/ ka wiſch prett Amo-\nziju to Kehnituu no Juha karrojs\ntas irr rakſtihts to Iſraêta Kel-\nnizu Laiku-Grahmatâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Joas atſmitge a-\ntaweem Tehweem/ un Jerobe-\nams fehdahs us winna Gohta\nKrehſlu. Bet Joas tappe eekſ-\nSamarijas aprakts pee teem I-\nfraêta Kehnixeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Elisus bija neiveffe-\nar fahdu Neweffelbu/ ar ko ta-\narrî nomire/ un Joas tas Iſre-\netâ Kehniſch nogahjepee ta/ u-\nrandaja winna Preeſchâ/ u-\nfazzija : Mans Tehws/ man-\nTehws! Iſraêta Ratti un win-\nna Jahtneeki."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Elisus fazzija us to-\nNemmweenu Stohpu/ un Bu-\ntas. Un kad wiſch to Sto-\npu un Bultas pee few nehme/"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiſch us t\nIſraêta Kehnixu : Uswelz t\nStohpu ar tawu Rohku/un ta-\nuswilke ar tawu Rohku. Un C-\nlisus likkefawu Rohkuuſta Kel-\nniza Rohku/"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
